body:
Also happened for me upon saving a model in Ubuntu 16.0.4, Python3, and Keras:
```python
Exception ignored in: <bound method BaseSession.__del__ of <tensorflow.python.client.session.Session object at 0x7f7c3e1fb2b0>>
Traceback (most recent call last):
  File "/usr/local/lib/python3.5/dist-packages/tensorflow/python/client/session.py", line 582, in __del__
UnboundLocalError: local variable 'status' referenced before assignment
```

```python
>>> tf.__version__
'1.0.1'
>>> keras.__version__
'2.0.4'
```
